title: Marathon Recovery - today I jog
description:
Back in Belfast, feeling a little jet lagged but not too bad. “Not that I would ever complain anyway”

Thanks so much for everybody’s support and love this week, I was asked to set up this page : https://ko-fi.com/roadtotokyo2020

I was hesistant to do that, but as I think it could help for now while support is a minimum. I went ahead and did that. 

Have a good day


Support the show
